---
title: Sri Lankan Beef & Coconut Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: This creamy coconut beef curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with bright
veggies and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the roasted peanuts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-sri-lankan-beef-curry-3ac2d5f6.jpg
